Light, Diet chicken cutlets. 
Ingredients 
30 g cereal

500 g chicken fillet 
50 g carrots 
15 g onion 
200 g zucchini 

Directions 
1.rub on a coarse grater, zucchini carefully squeeze the juice, minced fillet do. 
2.grated vegetables, minced chicken, corn flakes, add egg, salt to taste, add a little black pepper.
